PLDA (Probabilistic Linear Discriminant Analysis) weights for speaker
diarization, embedded in the dia binary via `include_bytes!`:

  models/plda/xvec_transform.npz   (134 KB; mean1, mean2, lda)
  models/plda/plda.npz             (134 KB; mu, tr, psi)
  models/plda/{mean1,mean2,lda,mu,tr,psi}.bin
                                    (raw f64 extractions of the above,
                                     compiled into the binary)

